text: Agustín María Lastagaray Toledano (born October 8, 1981) is an Argentine footballer who currently plays for El Linqueño in Torneo Argentino B. He started his professional career with Quilmes Atlético Club. In 2006, Lastargaray would be signed by Salvadoran Club C.D.
